Package rubank

package rubank
  • Class
    Description
    Account
    An abstract class representing a bank account.
    AccountDatabase
    A class representing a database of bank accounts.
    AccountDatabaseTest
    The AccountDatabaseTest class is a JUnit test class for testing the functionality of the AccountDatabase class.
    Campus
    Enum representing different campuses.
    Checking
    Represents a checking account, a type of bank account that allows transactions and provides an interest rate.
    CollegeChecking
    CollegeChecking class represents a checking account specifically designed for college students.
    Date
    The Date class is made for the Date object, holding pertinent information related to a Date such as the year, month, and day while also having getters and setters for those instance variables, helper methods like isLeapYear(), and overridden methods like equals(), and compareTo().
    DateTest
    The DateTest class is a JUnit test class for testing the functionality of the Date class.
    MoneyMarket
    The MoneyMarket class represents a MoneyMarket account at RU Bank, and it inherits the Savings class.
    Profile
    The Profile class represents a person's profile information including first name, last name, and date of birth.
    Savings
    The Savings class represents a Savings account at RU Bank, and it inherits the Account class.
    TransactionManagerController
    The controller class for Transaction Manager, defining functionalities for all buttons and Text Fields on the GUI
    TransactionManagerMain
